ce:section.ce:para:
CQDs were synthesized from bamboo leaves by hydrothermal treatment at 200°C for a period of 6h (Scheme 1
                        ). TEM image of as-prepared CQDs is shown in Fig. 1
                        . It is revealed that the CQDs are monodispersed particles in a spherical shape with diameter ranging from 2 to 6nm. The corresponding size distribution histogram is plotted in the inset of Fig. 1, from which the majority particle size distributed between 3.4 and 4.2nm is observed and average diameter is calculated to be 3.6nm.
